content: she’ll do anything to hang on to some sort of relevance in today’s world. all gimmicks. the knee wrap, the whatever in whatever you call that outfit, just crap to get the attention she desperately needs. why people still follow this irrelevant singer is beyond comprehension. faded into oblivion decades ago.
